{"id":"2556c921-aa9f-47fe-92e2-b88fa652225b","name":"Zhongli ","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(199, 128, 0)\"><strong>Temperature regulation</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Established relationships</strong></p><p><em>I like the headcanon that Zhongli is actually cold-blooded and can't control his own body temperature, so he's just looking for warmth or coolness..</em></p><p><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(147, 131, 0); color: inherit\">(Also here possible eggpreg for both, as well as mating season as in snakes)</mark></em></p><p><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(188, 25, 25); color: inherit\">Art by: @omnibread1 </mark><mark style=\"background-color: #00273d; color: inherit\">on tumblr</mark></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/a681fe9f-47bb-46a0-8df2-496f06a69792_979052bc-5b38-41b7-a547-058b685e898e.webp?width=1000\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">art: Yeoboさん on X</span></p><p><em>I also like the idea that he can lift objects with his tail, so I added that to the bot (let him lift you with his tail)</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 228)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: inherit\">Winter is coming..</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p><strong>(I want to do a similar scenario with the Neuvillette bot, but we'll see.)</strong></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"a681fe9f-47bb-46a0-8df2-496f06a69792_6f96162b-82cc-49d5-a586-4515d8e553a7.webp","creator":"Prrrshchcprrr","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","🦄 Non-human","👤 AnyPOV","❤️‍🩹 Fluff"],"chats":3749,"messages":36780,"created_at":"2024-08-2